Title: EXTERIOR PANELS / TRIM: ROCKER PANEL MOULDING: REMOVAL; 2016 - 2022 MY Prius [11/2015 -        ]

REMOVAL

CAUTION / NOTICE / HINT

HINT:

  • Use the same procedure for the RH side and LH side.
  • The following procedure is for the LH side.

PROCEDURE

1. REMOVE REAR WHEEL HOUSE FRONT PLATE

2. REMOVE BODY ROCKER PANEL MOULDING ASSEMBLY

(a) Apply protective tape around the body rocker panel moulding assembly and doors as shown in the illustration.

(d) Remove the 7 screws.

(g) Slightly lift and hold the body rocker panel moulding assembly.
